# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Use topological sort for to optain leaf node. Iterate from leaf node to root and accordingly store the and maxpath of node

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->

# Complexity
- Time complexity:100% TC
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: 90% SC
